										<li>Each persona can have its own display name, bio, and political placement.</li>
										<li>Personas are not burner accounts; they are first-class identity surfaces.</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</details>
						</div>
						<div class="surface-card band-card">
							<p class="band-kicker">Proof bundles</p>
							<details class="trust-accordion">
								<summary>View verification layers</summary>
								<div class="accordion-content">
									<ul>
										<li>INE scan for Mexican voter verification.</li>
										<li>Biometric gate and app-state auto-lock.</li>
										<li>QR export to share verified bundles offline.</li>
										<li>Custom surface builder to control what each context sees.</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</details>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
