					</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="section-intro">
						
							We enforce baseline rules through human review and automated signals. We also design for
							composable safety—labelers, user controls, and community-specific norms—so moderation
							is not a single gatekeeper.
						
					</p>
					<div class="band-grid">
						<div class="surface-card band-card">
							<p class="band-kicker">Baseline</p>
							<h3>Community Guidelines</h3>
							<p>
								
