									govern what we remove or limit on PARA services we operate.
								
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="surface-card band-card">
							<p class="band-kicker">Composable</p>
							<h3>Labelers and user controls</h3>
							<p>
								
									Where the protocol supports it, users can subscribe to additional labelers and adjust
									safety settings. Communities can add context on top of baseline rules.
								
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="docs-callout appeals-callout">
						<p>
							<strong>Appeals.</strong> If we restrict or suspend your account, you may appeal within fourteen (14) days. Late or bare appeals may be declined. We retain discretion to make final calls.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="trust-bands" id="verification">
				<div class="section-head">
