						<div class="eyebrow">03 / Verification</div>
						<h2 class="section-title">Trust without forced exposure.</h2>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="section-intro">
						
							Validation matters for civic participation, but not every user should have to expose
							their real name to participate. PARA holds both at once.
						
					</p>
