										<li>Access to verified-only communities and representative channels.</li>
										<li>Higher weight in certain aggregation or ranking surfaces.</li>
										<li>Reputation that persists across personas where you choose to link it.</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</details>
						</div>
						<div class="surface-card band-card">
							<p class="band-kicker">What anonymity protects</p>
